### Create new activity item [POST]

Posts Adds a new activity (river) item to the feed

+ Parameters

    + action (string, required) - action type
    + view (string, required) - river view
        + Default: `river/elements/layout`
    + subject_uid (string, required) - UID of the subject entity
    + object_uid (string, optional) - UID of the object entity
    + target_uid (string, optional) - UID of the target entity
    + annotation_uid (string, optional) - UID of the annotation


